title: Maldives GDP From Tertiary Industry
description: GDP from Services in Maldives increased to 55967 MVR Million in 2021 from 38113.20 MVR Million in 2020. GDP from Services in Maldives averaged 32192.06 MVR Million from 1995 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 58053 MVR Million in 2019 and a record low of 14720 MVR Million in 1995. This page provides - Maldives Gdp From Services- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Maldives Monetary Authority
